CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775830266
OL,3,CGladiators presenter Barney Walsh
OL,4,Cbanned from driving after speeding
OL,6,FMr Lewis said Walsh is "in a position"
OL,7,Fto pay the fixed penalty notice within
OL,8,F28 days.
OL,10,FWalsh, of Epping in Essex, is a
OL,11,Fpresenter and actor who has appeared
OL,12,Fin TV shows including Death in
OL,13,FParadise and Casualty.
OL,15,FHe has co-presented Gladiators with
OL,16,Fhis 65-year-old father since the show
OL,17,Fwas rebooted in early 2024.
OL,26,@nD@XOUnD@fO]
